{"id":11695,"name":"Twinsen","username":"Quetch","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/quetch/{size}/24543_2.png","created_at":"2007-12-19T10:04:56.000Z","cooked":"<p>[b]Little Big Adventure 2</p>\n<ul>\n<li>White T-Shirt Mod -[/b]</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"bbcode-b\"><span class=\"bbcode-u\">Description: </span></span></p>\n<p>This mod came to existence because of the original concept where Twinsen was supposed to wear a white T-Shirt. Such reference can still be seen in the games intro movie. Also, a preview of LBA2, also known to have been in beta stage has clearly shown screenshots where Twinsen was wearing his original white T-Shirt.</p>\n<p><span class=\"bbcode-u\"><span class=\"bbcode-b\">Note: </span></span></p>\n<p>The original version of LBA2 was meant to contain other different elements such as a modified ferry, gaining access to the top of the lighthouse, modified areas of some islands, a blue sky in the undergas level, etc. but unfortunately I could only bring Twinsens T-Shirt back <img src=\"https://forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p><span class=\"bbcode-u\"><span class=\"bbcode-b\">Installation:</span></span></p>\n<p>Extract the RESS.HQR file inside the archive into the LBA2/TO installation directory, overwriting the existing one. (Be sure to make a backup first!) Enjoy!</p>\n<p><a class=\"attachment\" href=\"/uploads/short-url/rVd9LPfYlmM9pLP5peuauAuH4w9.zip\">LBA2_WTSM.zip</a> (429 KB)</p>","post_number":1,"post_type":1,"posts_count":22,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T19:51:20.147Z","reply_count":19,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":14,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":165.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":11692,"topic_slug":"lba2-twinsens-white-t-shirt","display_username":"Twinsen","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":"","bookmarked":false,"raw":"[b]Little Big Adventure 2\n   - White T-Shirt Mod -[/b]\n\n[b][u]Description: [/u][/b]\n\nThis mod came to existence because of the original concept where Twinsen was supposed to wear a white T-Shirt. Such reference can still be seen in the game's intro movie. Also, a preview of LBA2, also known to have been in beta stage has clearly shown screenshots where Twinsen was wearing his original white T-Shirt.\n\n[u][b]Note: [/b][/u]\n\nThe original version of LBA2 was meant to contain other different elements such as a modified ferry, gaining access to the top of the lighthouse, modified areas of some islands, a blue sky in the undergas level, etc. but unfortunately I could only bring Twinsen's T-Shirt back :)\n\n[u][b]Installation:[/b][/u]\n\nExtract the 'RESS.HQR' file inside the archive into the LBA2/TO installation directory, overwriting the existing one. (Be sure to make a backup first!) Enjoy!\n\n[LBA2_WTSM.zip|attachment](upload://rVd9LPfYlmM9pLP5peuauAuH4w9.zip) (429 KB)","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":1595,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba2-twinsens-white-t-shirt/11692/1","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null,"can_vote":false}
{"id":309038,"name":null,"username":"xesf","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/xesf/{size}/122_2.png","created_at":"2007-12-22T11:46:52.000Z","cooked":"<p>Always give some screenshots.</p>\n<p>I think OBrasilo already did this a while ago, but still its a good mod to use for those who like to mod LBA2 instead of LBA1 <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/stuck_out_tongue.png?v=12\" title=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>Btw, I see you only change Twinsens outfit texture, right?!</p>","post_number":2,"post_type":1,"posts_count":22,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T18:14:12.304Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":0.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":11692,"topic_slug":"lba2-twinsens-white-t-shirt","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":1595,"username":"Quetch","name":"Twinsen","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/quetch/{size}/24543_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"Always give some screenshots.\n\nI think OBrasilo already did this a while ago, but still its a good mod to use for those who like to mod LBA2 instead of LBA1 :P\n\n\nBtw, I see you only change Twinsen's outfit texture, right?!","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"group_moderator":true,"user_id":463,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_hist