{"id":309044,"name":"","username":"elmuerte","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/elmuerte/{size}/27089_2.png","created_at":"2007-12-22T14:12:37.000Z","cooked":"<p>well, I was the first one to ever mod LBA2. I changed Twinsens wizard robe, gave it my avatar as pattern.</p>","post_number":3,"post_type":1,"posts_count":22,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T18:14:12.491Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":0.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":11692,"topic_slug":"lba2-twinsens-white-t-shirt","display_username":"","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":"staff","flair_url":"/uploads/default/original/3X/5/5/559743aa44a0676e04be9d54425231def12069c1.png","flair_bg_color":"","flair_color":"","flair_group_id":3,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":"","reply_to_user":{"id":1595,"username":"Quetch","name":"Twinsen","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/quetch/{size}/24543_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"well, I was the first one to ever mod LBA2. I changed Twinsen's wizard robe, gave it my avatar as pattern.","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":true,"admin":true,"staff":true,"user_id":1,"hidden":false,"trust_level":4,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba2-twinsens-white-t-shirt/11692/3","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
{"id":309045,"name":null,"username":"xesf","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/xesf/{size}/122_2.png","created_at":"2007-12-22T14:26:41.000Z","cooked":"<p>I think I remember that mod <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/stuck_out_tongue.png?v=12\" title=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>","post_number":4,"post_type":1,"posts_count":22,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T18:14:12.522Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":0.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":11692,"topic_slug":"lba2-twinsens-white-t-shirt","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":1595,"username":"Quetch","name":"Twinsen","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/quetch/{size}/24543_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"I think I remember that mod :p","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"group_moderator":true,"user_id":463,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba2-twinsens-white-t-shirt/11692/4","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
{"id":309183,"name":"Twinsen","username":"Quetch","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/quetch/{size}/24543_2.png","created_at":"2007-12-24T14:43:21.000Z","cooked":"<p>yeah, I just replaced the texture  but the hard thing was that pure white (255,255,255) didnt work  I figure pure white has some transparency problems as the gourad sharing was showing weird red-orange-brown-yellow patterns  like lava on the TShirt <img src=\"https://forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"> so what I did was take the LBA2 palette and pick the closest white that I could and the surprise was that it was exactly the white they used in the LBA2 preview <img src=\"https://forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/smiley.png?v=12\" title=\":smiley:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":smiley:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"> also, here are the shots :</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://forum.magicball.net/uploads/default/original/2X/f/f68efd46b8840054a36b99b62f3b2f76e4132396.jpeg\" alt=\"lba0.jpg\" data-base62-sha1=\"zb9OhzhVkurVowKeTIicI1PtRvo\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"><img src=\"https://forum.magicball.net/uploads/default/original/2X/9/9cd896b760896e661308195b08416e10c17c111d.jpeg\" alt=\"lba1.jpg\" data-base62-sha1=\"mnwwwCFVLKNWl6mkJdcQEiaVn8V\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></p>","post_number":5,"post_type":1,"posts_count":22,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T19:45:00.590Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":0.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":11692,"topic_slug":"lba2-twinsens-white-t-shirt","display_username":"Twinsen","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":"","reply_to_user":{"id":1595,"username":"Quetch","name":"Twinsen","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/quetch/{size}/24543_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"yeah, I just replaced the texture ... but the hard thing was that pure white (255,255,255) didn't work ... I figure pure white has some transparency problems as the gourad sharing was showing weird red-orange-brown-yellow patterns ... like lava on the TShirt :) so what I did was take the LBA2 palette and pick the closest white that I could and the surprise was that it was exactly the white they used in the LBA2 preview :D also, here are the shots :\n\n![lba0.jpg|640x480](upload://zb9OhzhVkurVowKeTIicI1PtRvo.jpeg)![lba1.jpg|640x480](upload://mnwwwCFVLKNWl6mkJdcQEiaVn8V.jpeg)","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":1595,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba2-twinsens-white-t-shirt/11692/5","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
{"id":309184,"name":null,"username":"leoboe","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/leoboe/{size}/479_2.png","created_at":"2007-12-24T14:48:56.000Z","cooked":"<p>you said that the pattern repeats itself with the texture and so it wont be possible to make him wear an MBN-Shirt.<br>\nBut what about the Parade-tunic then?<br>\nHas it got the same problem or would it be possible to add the MBN-Logo there? <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/stuck_out_tongue.png?v=12\" title=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>","post_number":6,"post_type":1,"posts_count":22,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T18:14:17.725Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":0.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":11692,"topic_slug":"lba2-twinsens-white-t-shirt","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":1595,"username":"Quetch","name":"Twinsen","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/quetch/{size}/24543_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"you said that the pattern repeats itself with the texture and so it won't be possible to make him wear an MBN-Shirt.\nBut what about the Parade-tunic then?\nHas it got the same problem or would it be possible to add the MBN-Logo there? :p","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":2284,"hidden":false,"trust_level":1,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_